clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: Used as an adjunct to the standard therapy of inhaled steroids with inhaled long and or short acting beta agonists

contraindications.disease: Side effects include headache abdominal or stomach pain cough dental pain dizziness fever heartburn skin rash stuffy nose weakness or unusual tiredness
contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Pranlukast is a cysteinyl leukotriene receptor 1 antagonist
